public interface XTerm
extends java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable

Constraints constrain XTerms. Thus XTerms are the basic building blocks of constraints.This interface should be implemented by the terms specific to all constraint systems. Two different implementations of XTerm should *never* be mixed.

Author:
njnystrom, vj
